## 3 Â· Important Series & Their Values

| Series | Closed form |
|--------|-------------|
| <m>\sum_{n=0}^{\infty} x^n</m> | <m>\dfrac{1}{1-x}</m>, for <m>|x|<1</m> |
| <m>\sum_{n=1}^{\infty} \dfrac{1}{n^2}</m> | <m>\dfrac{\pi^2}{6}</m> |
| <m>\sum_{n=1}^{\infty} \dfrac{1}{n^4}</m> | <m>\dfrac{\pi^4}{90}</m> |
| <m>\sum_{n=0}^{\infty} \dfrac{x^n}{n!}</m> | <m>e^x</m> |
| <m>\sum_{n=0}^{\infty} (-1)^n \dfrac{x^{2n}}{(2n)!}</m> | <m>\cos x</m> |
| <m>\sum_{n=0}^{\infty} (-1)^n \dfrac{x^{2n+1}}{(2n+1)!}</m> | <m>\sin x</m> |

